1. Bxh7+
{ A knight that can hop to g5, the queen ready to go to the h-file, a dark-squared bishop on the c1-h6 diagonal, a pawn on e5 controlling f6 and no light-squared bishop reaching the b1-h7 diagonal for Black soon. The greek gift sacrifice has to work ! }
1... Kxh7 2. Ng5+ Kg8
{ 11...Kg6  shouldn't work with so many pieces attacking and it doesn't. E.g.  12.Qg4   12.h4  is another typical reinforcing idea.  Rh8  13.Qg4  f5  14.Qg3  f4  15.Qg4  +-  12...f5  13.Qf4  +- }
